Description:
Ensure getcwd(NULL, 0) returns a buffer allocated by malloc().

Files:
lib/getcwd-lgpl.c
m4/getcwd.m4

Depends-on:
unistd
strdup          [test $REPLACE_GETCWD = 1]

configure.ac:
gl_FUNC_GETCWD_LGPL
if test $REPLACE_GETCWD = 1; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([getcwd-lgpl])
fi
gl_UNISTD_MODULE_INDICATOR([getcwd])

